
Runj se khugar hua insaan to mit jaata hai runj 
Mushkilein mujh par padi itni ke aasaan ho gayi

- 'Ghalib'

Translation <a href="http://kgfindia.com/great-injustice.php"> from here</a>

When a person is habituated of sorrows
Then sorrows disappear
So many difficulties fell upon me 
That everything became easy.

